  "3245640": {
    "name": "Starfinder: Afterlight",
    "steam_appid": 3245640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/53bd69d7e6328ead76ad3370024c9c51.avif?t=1772487120\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras_big/53bd69d7e6328ead76ad3370024c9c51.webp?t=1772487120 width=1560 height=405 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>集结你的队伍，深入契约诸界，谱写关于意料之外的英雄、宇宙的奇迹，以及彼此间羁绊的故事。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星系面临灭顶之灾，你的舰长凭空消失，末日近在眼前。在群星间组建一支由奇人异士组成的小队，在这款单人团队制RPG中走上传奇之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/6212646f84bad8a9910f425eed7a0a7f.poster.avif?t=1772487120\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/6212646f84bad8a9910f425eed7a0a7f.webm?t=1772487120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/6212646f84bad8a9910f425eed7a0a7f.mp4?t=1772487120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到散落群星之间的6个独特伙伴，从仿生人刺客到秘术师先知。每位队友都会带来专属的故事和道德困境。你在每一场胜利与失利之间与他们建立的羁绊将会决定他们的命运，以及整个星系的存亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/f6c05579bc1861b9f63f17b72e72dca0.avif?t=1772487120\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras_big/f6c05579bc1861b9f63f17b72e72dca0.webp?t=1772487120 width=1560 height=416 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用《Starfinder》中的职业：士兵、使节、特工、秘术师、恒星武士和织维巫师，投身回合制策略战斗之中。利用Paizo备受好评的三行动系统，将无穷无尽的丰富战术化为可能。提升等级，收集异星装备，与各种各样的敌人战斗——从地狱骑士到数字幽灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/60dd02157343d250137cb482fd6a5094.avif?t=1772487120\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras_big/60dd02157343d250137cb482fd6a5094.webp?t=1772487120 width=1560 height=427 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验错综复杂的叙事；你的选择在其中举足轻重。万事皆无禁忌，万事皆有后果。伸出援手或是牟取私利，仁慈宽恕或是无情复仇。派系会记得你的选择，队友会衡量你的真心，而你的传奇尽由你一人书写。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/9e9526183e43c0cb5fc38a5a056019a4.avif?t=1772487120\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras_big/9e9526183e43c0cb5fc38a5a056019a4.webp?t=1772487120 width=1560 height=415 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 Absalom 空间站到 Eox 的不死帝国，从数字神明到宇宙巨龙。在40到60小时的冒险中，探索魔法与技术交相辉映的契约诸界。在这个宇宙中，一切事物皆有可能，而且一切事物都有可能想要杀死你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/604e3002ecde6a966be400e7d44f8682.avif?t=1772487120\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras_big/604e3002ecde6a966be400e7d44f8682.webp?t=1772487120 width=1560 height=510 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245640/extras/6e53601788b625bb21159e0a461d9080.avif?t=1772487120\" width=1600 height=186 /></span></h2>",
